London - Silvio Berlusconi , Italy &apos;s three @-@ time prime minister and the country &apos;s dominant politician for two decades , has now been convicted and sentenced to four years in prison - a sentence since reduced to one year . but few people in Italy - or in Europe - believe that Berlusconi will fade from Italian , or European , politics anytime soon .
